OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning very
OL,6,Fwindy, with inland gales, perhaps
OL,7,Fsevere. Blustery rain and showers
OL,8,Fquickly moving through before
OL,9,Fmidnight. Turning drier and colder,
OL,10,Fwith winds easing through the early
OL,11,Fhours of Monday, but perhaps the odd
OL,12,Fshower still possible, wintry over
OL,13,Fhills.
OL,14,
OL,15,CSunday:FBright and breezy Easter
OL,16,FSunday with some sunny spells to
OL,17,Fstart. Cloud then thickening, with
OL,18,Fblustery showers during the afternoon,
OL,19,Fbefore late sunny spells follow.
OL,20,FFeeling cooler than Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
